text:
Decent chicken rice for daily meal. Better options in the market nearby.

Boiled dumplings were not good - the skin is too thick without sufficient meat filling.

Staff are friendly
A nice gem, no crowd due to the location and but chicken rice is surprisingly tasty! Good to try if you stay nearby and portion is decent too.. will recommend!
Chicken rice tasted average. There was also no minced ginger. Gizzards came in a mountain for only $1. Friendly staff.
An average chicken rice—portion was quite small and nothing particularly special. Decent if you’re just looking for a quick bite.

Hainanese Chicken surprisingly good and using fresh chicken instead of the usual frozen ones we see all over these days. Wanton soup can give it a miss, nothing fancy, definitely not a wow. It's usually understaffed and avoid lunch timings.
